name: flaightidl
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "flaightidl" %}
{% set version = "0.1.1" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: f19969361b2167fc349a8ddef97833006083ebc7a39eef69f4968d6c987f7f89

build:
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"
  noarch: python

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.6
  run:
    - protobuf >=3.5.0,<4.0.0
    - python >=3.6

test:
  imports:
    - flyteidl
    - flyteidl.admin
    - flyteidl.core
    - flyteidl.datacatalog
    - flyteidl.event
    - flyteidl.plugins
    - flyteidl.plugins.sagemaker
    - flyteidl.service
    - validate

about:
  home: https://latch.bio 
  license: Apache-2.0
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: "IDL for Flyte Platform (Latch fork)"

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ayushkamat
    - maximsmol
